ğŸ§  3. SYSTEM WORKFLOW


Front ultrasonic sensor detects your hand
â†’ Lid opens
â†’ Timer starts
â†’ After 3 seconds (no hand) â†’ lid closes


Top ultrasonic sensor measures bin depth
â†’ Calculates percentage fill
â†’ Displays on LCD


If fillPercent >= 100%
â†’ Plays Super Mario Theme once
â†’ LCD shows status
â†’ Lid still works normally



