â— 9. TROUBLESHOOTING
Buzzer very quiet


You might be using an active buzzer


Solution: replace with passive buzzer


Or I can give you "active buzzer" version (beep only)


LCD blank
Try:
LiquidCrystal_I2C lcd(0x3F, 16, 2);

Servo twitches


Use separate 5V power supply for servo


Connect grounds together


Level reading always 100%


Incorrect BIN_HEIGHT_CM


Sensor too close to lid


Obstructions inside bin


Mario song stops other functions


Song uses delay


Use "non-blocking music player" if needed
(ask me if you want this upgrade)



ğŸ“˜ 10. MAINTENANCE


